Thom Adcox-Hernandez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thom_Adcox-Hernandez 0 Thom Adcox-Hernandez is an American actor and voice actor known for his roles as Brian in the prime-time soap opera, Falcon Crest and the voices of Felix the Cat in The Twisted Tales of Felix the Cat and Lexington on Gargoyles.
